{"tid":791822,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"逃稅風波後首發聲 李晨：冰冰最近有點事","createTime":"2018-08-24T06:05:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T16:07:53.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f101c4799e54c8b0662cd769876790cb7ca02ce9","tid":791822,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:05:10.000Z","msg":"內地女星范冰冰自從捲入逃稅風波後，一直未有公開露面，行蹤備受關注，其男友李晨在事件發生後，亦未有在公開場合現身。不過昨日有一位名為「周於斯UC」的網民，聲稱跟李晨在關島敍舊，並附上一張二人在潛水艇的合照。<br />\n<br />\n本身是旅遊攝影師的周於斯表示要幫李晨傳話：「冰冰最近有點事兒，在內地尚好，希望大家不要擔心。」如果屬實，李晨便是在女友捲入逃稅風波後首次發聲。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/UcG9Kd775sz1p8wT7aCz6w--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thesun.hk.com/9eb124b8ded1067442481d8f90833716\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FUcG9Kd775sz1p8wT7aCz6w--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F9eb124b8ded1067442481d8f90833716&h=9b0e3cfc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dec14aa6f4e7406fd54d170ab573aa12f11e6699","tid":791822,"uid":98386,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:32:03.000Z","msg":"俾領導輪完再交啲錢就沒事兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5262dbb47fe75aa35c190aff494dbaeff26b1763","tid":791822,"uid":58552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:53:17.000Z","msg":"西隧"},{"pid":"76d9282cad2432d897f50771791b1361d41dfaa3","tid":791822,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dec14aa6f4e7406fd54d170ab573aa12f11e6699","tid":791822,"uid":98386,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:32:03.000Z","msg":"俾領導輪完再交啲錢就沒事兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:55:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b96965ce248427b4641343852f2283421acec30c","tid